data.description: Experience the serenity of Waterfront property! Nature at it's finest, with birds chirping and ducks quacking as you sip on your morning coffee. Imagine dinner on your back deck, overlooking the delta, with the sun setting behind Mt. Diablo in the background. This home offers that and so much more! Fish right off the dock, or jump in your boat and troll around the slough with your fishing pole out. Are you an avid watersports enthusiast? Under 10 minutes to fast water with some of the best waterways in the country! Enjoy creating meals in the updated kitchen layout, which includes beautiful grey granite countertops, clean white cabinets, and updated flooring that continues into the living room and master bedroom. Multiple windows in the kitchen and living area provide you with stunning panoramic views of the delta, local mountain range, and open farm fields. This home sits on a large 10,000 sq. ft. lot with plenty of space to park your RV, Boat, or other toys, but don't forget the oversized 2 car garage as well. The dock comes with a fully covered birth and a boat hoist. Along with all of that, come home to your spa and wind down after a long day of work. What more could you want?
